data.description: Charming Three-Bedroom Home on a Beautiful Lot!  Don't be fooled-this is much larger than it appears! Features include a family room and full bath with walk-in shower in the lower level; fully equipped kitchen with stainless steel appliances; dishwasher- 2022; two spacious bedrooms and hardwood floors on first floor; bonus room on second floor could be a study, playroom or walk-in closet; coved ceilings in living room and dining room; private wooded rear yard with natural stone patio; fireplace in living room conveniently located to downtown Cincinnati, Clifton, the new College Hill businesses and Cross County Highway! Ready for a Buyer!!
